headline: Here's What to Expect From Wynn Resorts' Next Earnings Report
summary: Wynn Resorts is scheduled to announce its fourth-quarter results soon, and analysts forecast a double-digit decline in the company’s bottom-line figure.

headline: CFOs On the Move: Week ending Jan. 16
summary: Paramount Skydance names a permanent CFO amid Warner Bros. acquisition attempts, Wynn Resorts promotes an insider to the top finance spot and Yale University’s finance chief is set to retire in June.
